- This way.

262
00:19:56,720 --> 00:20:00,120
Classmate, find a suitable place to stand.

263
00:20:02,520 --> 00:20:04,319
Come on, quickly.

264
00:20:04,319 --> 00:20:06,139
Xu Shanshan, line up by height.

265
00:20:06,139 --> 00:20:08,380
I am lining up by height.

266
00:20:08,380 --> 00:20:10,879
- You're on tiptoe. You go down, you go down.
- I'm not. Why?

267
00:20:10,879 --> 00:20:12,460
- I'm taller than you.
- Don't move.

268
00:20:12,460 --> 00:20:14,840
Don't move, don't move. I told you not to move.

269
00:20:14,840 --> 00:20:17,620
Get ready. Three,

270
00:20:19,339 --> 00:20:21,040
two,

271
00:20:21,040 --> 00:20:22,839
one.

272
00:20:22,839 --> 00:20:25,639
What are you doing? I told you not to move.

273
00:20:25,639 --> 00:20:28,140
Come. Stand straight.

274
00:20:28,140 --> 00:20:31,020
I told you not to move. Don't move. Stand straight.

275
00:20:31,020 --> 00:20:33,039
Xu Shanshan, are you willing to come down?

276
00:20:33,039 --> 00:20:35,800
- Jiang Xile, why did you push me?
- Who pushed you?

277
00:20:35,800 --> 00:20:37,920
- It was you. Who else could it be?
- It wasn't me.

278
00:20:37,920 --> 00:20:40,460
Xu Shanshan, you're already down. Don't climb up again.

279
00:20:40,460 --> 00:20:42,039
- Let go of me, Lu Liuliu.
- Don't move.

280
00:20:42,039 --> 00:20:43,460
Stand still. Don't sway.

281
00:20:43,460 --> 00:20:45,780
Hurry up, we're taking a photo.

282
00:20:45,780 --> 00:20:47,639
Be happy.

283
00:20:47,639 --> 00:20:50,140
Ready.

284
00:20:50,140 --> 00:20:52,059
Three,

285
00:20:52,059 --> 00:20:53,480
two,

286
00:20:53,480 --> 00:20:55,400
one.

287
00:20:57,499 --> 00:21:00,356
♫ How did I meet you? ♫

288
00:21:00,356 --> 00:21:07,736
♫ Flipping through the pages of our story ♫

289
00:21:07,736 --> 00:21:10,920
Just how much do you hate me?

290
00:21:12,191 --> 00:21:19,105
♫ Even if the storm comes again, I don't want to hide ♫

291
00:21:19,105 --> 00:21:26,720
♫ Under your eaves, we meet without feeling like strangers now ♫

292
00:21:26,720 --> 00:21:28,380
Jiang Xile, come here quickly.

293
00:21:28,380 --> 00:21:31,260
The party is about to start.

294
00:21:42,843 --> 00:21:46,800
♫ You are the love that's out of reach ♫

295
00:21:46,800 --> 00:21:48,960
The opposite room.

296
00:21:48,960 --> 00:21:52,179
We'll see each other from time to time.

297
00:21:52,179 --> 00:21:55,139
How can I live in the future?

298
00:21:55,139 --> 00:22:02,003
♫ Endless like sailing, not afraid of being blown away by the wind ♫

299
00:22:02,003 --> 00:22:09,159
♫ The moonlight confesses in my place as I wake up ♫

300
00:22:09,159 --> 00:22:12,180
Line up by height. Tall ones stand at the back.

301
00:22:12,180 --> 00:22:14,700
Other classmates, hurry up, hurry!

302
00:22:15,739 --> 00:22:18,779
Switch places according to your height.

303
00:22:19,760 --> 00:22:21,720
Xu Shanshan, line up by height.

304
00:22:21,720 --> 00:22:22,959
I am lining up by height.

305
00:22:22,959 --> 00:22:26,220
- You're on tiptoe. Get down. Get down.
- I'm not. Why?

306
00:22:26,220 --> 00:22:28,000
I told you not to move. Don't move.

307
00:22:28,000 --> 00:22:30,620
Ready. Three,

308
00:22:30,620 --> 00:22:31,980
two,

309
00:22:31,980 --> 00:22:33,712
one.

310
00:22:35,540 --> 00:22:37,560
Told you not to move. Why are you still moving?

311
00:22:37,560 --> 00:22:39,580
Xu Shanshan, are you willing to get down?

312
00:22:39,580 --> 00:22:41,560
Jiang Xile, why did you push me?

313
00:22:41,560 --> 00:22:43,400
- Who pushed you?
- It was you.

314
00:22:43,400 --> 00:22:45,219
All right, all right, stop arguing. Line up.

315
00:22:45,219 --> 00:22:47,020
Don't climb up anymore. Ready.

316
00:22:47,020 --> 00:22:48,239
Three,

317
00:22:48,239 --> 00:22:49,600
two,

318
00:22:49,600 --> 00:22:51,120
one.

319
00:22:51,120 --> 00:22:56,584
♫ I'm blessed to encounter a meaningful bond ♫

320
00:22:57,671 --> 00:23:01,835
♫ Saying, "I like you," comes too late ♫

321
00:23:01,835 --> 00:23:05,274
♫ Thinking back to when we first met ♫

322
00:23:05,274 --> 00:23:10,126
♫ I had sweaty palms and my senses awestruck ♫

323
00:23:10,126 --> 00:23:16,115
♫ Ten years of missed opportunity, now reunited with regret ♫

324
00:23:16,115 --> 00:23:22,604
♫ All at once, overnight, I realized I had loved you deeply then ♫

325
00:23:22,604 --> 00:23:29,356
♫ Memories of you laughing, crying, and forgotten feelings ♫

326
00:23:29,356 --> 00:23:33,656
♫ The most intimate thoughts turned into nothingness ♫

327
00:23:33,656 --> 00:23:36,435
♫ Missing you is hard to endure ♫

328
00:23:36,435 --> 00:23:42,733
♫ You haunt my dreams, yet you completely ignore me ♫

329
00:23:42,733 --> 00:23:49,399
♫ It dawned on me overnight that after all the twists and turns, I still love you deeply ♫

330
00:23:49,399 --> 00:23:52,261
♫ Back then, I was oblivious, pushing you away ♫
